Usage: report_oa_lib [-help] <lib_name> [-header ] [-filter {cdsinfo | compression | constraint_groups | property | tech_graph}]

-help          # Prints out the command usage
<lib_name>     # Specifies the name of a library to be updated
               # (string, required)
-filter {cdsinfo compression constraint_groups property tech_graph}
               # To filter (enum_list, optional)
-header        # Header (bool, optional)